                      "content": "01 / WORK",
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "500",
                      "letterSpacing": 0.048
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "I0aBw",
                      "name": "title",
                      "fill": "#111111",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 720,
                      "content": "Case work shaped by\noperating reality, not\nproduct theatre",
                      "lineHeight": 1.1,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 64,
                      "fontWeight": "700",
                      "letterSpacing": -0.01
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "qlYHH",
                      "name": "sub",
                      "fill": "#111827",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 640,
                      "content": "Each project is framed around the system constraint, the product mechanism introduced, and the measurable shift in behavior or performance that followed.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.65,
                      "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                      "fontSize": 16
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "uGwpA",
                      "name": "introAnn",
                      "fill": "#6B7280",
                      "content": "// systems > features",
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "500",
                      "letterSpacing": 0.048
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "id": "ltTtB",
                      "name": "introSig",
                      "fill": "#E5E7EB",
                      "width": 180,
                      "height": 1
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "QMDJW",
                  "name": "cases",
                  "width": 720,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 38,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "LyNn7",
                      "name": "case1",
                      "width": 640,
                      "fill": "#F4F6F8",
                      "stroke": {
                        "align": "inside",
                        "thickness": 1,
                        "fill": "#D1D5DB"
                      },
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 16,
                      "padding": 24,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "FEZ4g",
                          "name": "c1label",
                          "fill": "#6B7280",
                          "content": "system · workflow · automation",
                          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "600",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.048
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "5QqHe",
                          "name": "c1t",
                          "fill": "#111111",
                          "content": "Zigtex",
                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 20,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "k6PFq",
                          "name": "c1d",
                          "fill": "#111827",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": 640,
                          "content": "The problem was volume without coordination: operators were moving fast, but decisions fragmented under pressure. I led the product and systems design of an AI-assisted workflow layer that standardized actions, exposed edge cases, and made exception handling legible. The result was a daily operating system that processed 10k+ automated actions, improved efficiency by 70%, and kept trust intact as the workflow scaled.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.65,
                          "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                          "fontSize": 18
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "BRBKj",
                          "name": "c1m",
                          "fill": "#6B7280",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": 580,
                          "content": "scale / reliability / automation",
                          "lineHeight": 1.5,
                          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "500"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "mKDCC",
                      "name": "case2",
                      "width": 620,
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                      "stroke": {
                        "align": "inside",
                        "thickness": 1,
                        "fill": "#F3F4F6"
                      },
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 14,
                      "padding": 24,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "pnPpK",
                          "name": "c2label",
                          "fill": "#6B7280",
                          "content": "workflow · instrumentation · operations",
                          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "500",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.048
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "Idpau",
                          "name": "c2t",
                          "fill": "#111111",
                          "content": "OpsGraph",
                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 20,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "TmYWs",
                          "name": "c2d",
                          "fill": "#111827",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": 640,
                          "content": "Teams were reacting to isolated incidents instead of managing the system that produced them. I shaped a product layer that connected demand patterns, handoff delays, and operational interventions into one shared view, giving engineering and operations a common language for prioritization. That system shifted reviews from reactive debugging to deliberate flow design, materially improving response quality and operational focus.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.65,
                          "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                          "fontSize": 18
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "nxjzY",
                          "name": "c2m",
                          "fill": "#6B7280",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": 580,
                          "content": "diagnosis / planning / service flow",
                          "lineHeight": 1.5,
                          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "500",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.048
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "JnTIz",
                          "name": "c2ann",
                          "fill": "#6B7280",
                          "content": "// built to expose the system, not decorate it",
                          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "500",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.048
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "7ICvB",
                      "name": "case3",
                      "width": 620,
                      "fill": "#FAFBFC",
                      "stroke": {
                        "align": "inside",
                        "thickness": 1,
                        "fill": "#F3F4F6"
                      },
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 18,
                      "padding": 24,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "ZpzXP",
                          "name": "c3label",
                          "fill": "#6B7280",
                          "content": "platform · governance · trust",
                          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "500",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.048
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "awu6c",
                          "name": "c3t",
                          "fill": "#111111",
                          "content": "Trust Console",
                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 20,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "CGdg0",
                          "name": "c3d",
                          "fill": "#111827",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": 640,
                          "content": "As AI actions grew more powerful, the real challenge was not generation but governance. I drove the design of a review and control layer that surfaced confidence, override paths, and failure modes in ways operators could act on quickly. The system reduced ambiguity around automation, improved operational confidence, and gave leadership a defensible model for scaling AI without hiding risk.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.65,
                          "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                          "fontSize": 18
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "zxfAp",
                          "name": "c3m",
                          "fill": "#6B7280",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": 580,
                          "content": "trust / override / auditability",
                          "lineHeight": 1.5,
                          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "500",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.048
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "pKCWO",
                          "name": "c3ann",
                          "fill": "#6B7280",
                          "content": "// reliability includes visible escape hatches",
                          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "500",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.048
                        }
                      ]
                    }
